  {
    "hotel_id": "62304",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/jw-marriott-hotel-jakarta_11/hotel/jakarta-id.html",
    "name": "JW Marriott Hotel Jakarta",
    "detail": "Located at Kuningan, a great part of Jakarta. There is a walk walking distance away (yes, walkable in Jakarta) which is very rare despite the traffic. It's fair, but not the exclusive Grand Indonesia Mall. Even if on require to go to GI, its about a 15minutes cab ride away. For business travelers, it's is ideal. Secuirty is extremely tight, as compared to the other Jakarta Hotels. Staffs are very friendly and helpful. There is a good spread of morning buffet breakfast. All and all, the experience is great. The rooms are clean, new, and very comfortable. The pool wasn't great. It looks like it either neglected or under maintenance. I trust its the latter. Gym is rather sufficient and fair. For a simple cardio workout, I guess it good enough.",
